text: Hi Qudrat, How's it going? I am told that you are interested in a career as a compositor? Just to let you know a little bit about myself; I am a lead compositor at Framestore in London, currently working on Wonder Woman 2. In January I am moving to Australia to work on some films (might be Marvel) but the titles are all a secret at the moment!
Hi Neil, I'm really good thank you. That is so cooooool, you're working on Wonder Woman 2!!
Are you moving to Australia because of work or did you want to move to Australia and then look for a job there.

Sorry i have a lot of questions. I should introduce myself, I am a first year student at Brunel University currently studying VFX and through a university project I started looking at different jobs within the industry and have become really interested in compositing and the process involved within it.
Can I ask why you decided to become a compositor?
